title: Drake's New Album & Living Drug Free
description:
Tasia opens up about her experience coming off anti-depressants and gives an update on Greenly's new school. Camo shares their thoughts on Drake's new album and hints at what the future of the podcast looks like.
Go to TalkSpace.com and use code UNFAZED to get $100 off of your first month.
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
If you like the show, telling a friend about it would be helpful! You can text, email, Tweet, or send this link to a friend: https://bit.ly/UnfazedandUnbotheredPodcast
